    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a mechanically sorted example of Porsche\u2019s wide-body, all-wheel-drive platform. Powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, the powerplant delivers 320hp through a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. Essential preventative maintenance is complete, featuring an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS). The chassis maintains its signature poise via a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, recently refreshed with Bilstein B6 dampers for improved rebound control. The viscous-coupling AWD system ensures optimal torque distribution, complemented by 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for superior thermal capacity. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the engine pull is linear and the hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and leak-free.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
