    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality, having been meticulously cared for by a non-smoking owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected road-wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery remains supple and free of significant wear, while all electronic features\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, benefiting from a documented history of regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Whether you\u2019re looking for a reliable commuter or a stylish weekend cruiser, this car delivers a smooth, quiet ride that feels solid on the road. It\u2019s a turnkey opportunity for a buyer who values both aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 38500.0,
